  # out of 17 SDG goals roboguy helps in:

- SDG 3 — Good Health & Well-Being

How Robo Guy helps:

Reduces emotional distress and isolation

Promotes mental health, routine, and self-care

Provides early emotional support before crises escalate

 Robo Guy acts as a first layer of emotional well-being support.

- SDG 4 — Quality Education

How Robo Guy helps:

Motivates students

Encourages discipline and focus

Supports learning through emotional stability

 Students learn better when they feel supported.

- SDG 8 — Decent Work & Economic Growth

How Robo Guy helps:

Builds discipline, consistency, and responsibility

Supports young people developing career habits

Reduces burnout and disengagement

 Emotionally stable youths become productive adults.

- SDG 10 — Reduced Inequalities

How Robo Guy helps:

Provides support to youths who lack access to mentors or counselors

Works across cultures and languages

Makes emotional support accessible and affordable

 Support should not be a privilege.

- SDG 11 — Sustainable Cities & Communities

How Robo Guy helps:

Strengthens emotional resilience in communities

Supports youths facing urban stress, loneliness, and pressure

Encourages positive social behavior

 Healthy communities start with healthy individuals.

- SDG 16 — Peace, Justice & Strong Institutions

How Robo Guy helps:

Encourages empathy, self-control, and ethical decision-making

Reduces emotional-driven conflict and violence

Promotes personal responsibility and respect

Peace begins with emotional intelligence.
